French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 275, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_I_of_Greece\", \"score\": 0.6366606336264803, \"rank\": 0.3667550856055445, \"text\": \"Prince William\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_I_of_Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_I_of_Greece\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Princess\", \"from\": 207, \"to\": 219}, {\"ngram\": \"Wales\", \"from\": 223, \"to\": 228}, {\"ngram\": \"her kids\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 302}, {\"ngram\": \"her health condition\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said, \\\"I am sure Kate would love to go to Paris with William to watch some events but whether she does or not would depend on the advice of her doctors.\\\"\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 385, \"end\": 389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Austen\", \"score\": 0.9264314548524631, \"rank\": 0.07927413250707262, \"text\": \"Kate\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Austen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Austen\"}, {\"begin\": 410, \"end\": 415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999936569256481, \"rank\": 6.3431145651847376e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"William\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"some events\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 449}, {\"ngram\": \"the advice\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"her doctors\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The royal author added, \\\"It was great to see her at Trooping the Colour and presenting the trophy to Carlos Alcaraz at Wimbledon but she will be pacing herself and not doing too much too soon because of her cancer diagnosis.\\\"\", \"from\"